1. *Gledaš* li televiziju svakog dana? (Are you watching TV every day?)
2. Ona *gleda* u tebe sa velikim zanimanjem. (She is looking at you with great interest.)
3. On *gleda* njene ruke u čudu. (He is looking at her hands in amazement.)
4. *Gledaš* li zvezde u noći? (Are you looking at the stars at night?)
5. Ona *gledala* u nebo i sanjala. (She was looking at the sky and dreaming.)
6. *Gledaš* li u pravcu kuće? (Are you looking in the direction of home?)